Bradley D. Goskowicz

Age : 60Public asset : 30,000 USDLinked companies : No connection available 





Summary 



Mr. Bradley D. Goskowicz is Independent Director at MOCON, Inc. and Chief Executive Officer at Microbiologics, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at MOCON, Inc.Mr. Goskowicz was previously employed as Head-Sales & Marketing by Johnson & Johnson, Head-Sales & Marketing by Medtronic, Inc., President by US Speedskating, Vice President-Marketing by ABIOMED, Inc., and VP-Marketing & Clinical Site Development by Myocor, Inc.



